M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- Is this feature currently used (if free)?
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- Will making it paid hurt retention?"
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|**agt asks:**
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|"**Usage pricing details:**
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- Usage metric: (seats, API calls, storage, transactions, etc.)
