M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- Expected ARPU change: $current → $new
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|**Expansion potential:**
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- As customers grow usage, will ARPU increase?"
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|**agt asks:**
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|"**Discount details:**
M|finance-based-pricing-advisor|- Discount type: (annual prepay, volume, promotional)
